<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <%- include ('./partials/head') %>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/forms.css" />
    <script src="/js/registerValidation.js"></script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include ('./partials/header') %>

    <main class="form-main">

      <section class="section-form">
        <div class="bg-light-blue br-10">

          <div>
            <% if(locals.errors){ errors.forEach(error => {%>
          <p class="font-navy"><%= error.msg %></p>
          <% }) } %>
          </div>
          
          <form
            class="form"
            action="/usuarios/registro"
            method="POST"
            enctype="multipart/form-data"
          >
            <h2 class="w-100">Registrate</h2>
            <div class="w-100 fx-align-center p-8">
              <input
                class="form-inp"
                type="text"
                name="first_name"
                id="firstName"
                placeholder="Nombre"
                value="<%= locals.old && old.firstName ? old.firstName : ''%>"
              />
            </div>

            <div class="w-100 fx-align-center p-8">
              <input
                class="form-inp"
                type="text"
                name="last_name"
                id="lastName"
                placeholder="Apellido"
                value="<%= locals.old && old.lastName ? old.lastName : ''%>"
              />
            </div>

            <div class="w-100 fx-align-center p-8">
              <input
                class="form-inp"
                type="mail"
                placeholder="Correo electrónico"
                name="email"
                id="email"
                value="<%= locals.old && old.email ? old.email : ''%>"
              />
            </div>

            <div class="w-100 fx-align-center p-8">
              <input
                class="form-inp"
                type="number"
                name="dni"
                id="dni"
                placeholder="Documento"
                value="<%= locals.old && old.dni ? old.dni : ''%>"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="w-100 fx-align-center p-8">
              <input
                class="form-inp"
                type="text"
                name="address"
                id="address"
                placeholder="Domicilio"
                value="<%= locals.old && old.address ? old.address : ''%>"
              />
            </div>

            <div class="w-100 fx-align-center p-8">
              <input
                class="form-inp"
                type="date"
                name="birthdate"
                id="birthdate"
                value="<%= locals.old && old.birthdate ? old.birthdate : ''%>"
              />
            </div>

            <div class="w-100 fx-align-center p-8">
              <input
                class="form-inp"
                type="password"
                name="password"
                id="password"
                placeholder="Contraseña"
                size="15" 
                maxlength="64" 
                />
            </div>
            <div class="w-100 fx-align-center p-8">
              <progress max="100" value="0" id="meter"></progress>
              <span id="spanPassword"></span>
            </div>

            <div class="flex fx-wrap w-100 fx-align-center p-8">
              <label for="profile_image" class="w-100"
                >Imagen de Perfil:
              </label>
              <div class="w-100 p-8">
                <input type="file" name="profile_image" id="profile_image" />
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="w-100 fx-align-center p-8">
              <div class="form-inp flex">
                <input class="w-25" type="checkbox" required />
                <p class="w-75" for="checkpoint">
                  Al continuar, doy fe de entender y aceptar la política de
                  privacidad, los términos y condiciones y los términos de uso
                  del sitio web. Al clickear “únete ahora” reconozco aceptar
                  formar parte del programa de beneficios de Take off Surf y
                  recibir ofertas exclusivas en mi correo electrónico. Puede
                  desuscibirse en cualquier momento clickeando elboton
                  “desuscribir” ubicado en el final de los correos electrónicos
                  recibidos.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="w-100 fx-align-center p-8">
              <button class="form-button" type="submit">Enviar</button>
            </div>

            <div class="w-100 fx-align-center p-8">
              <button class="form-button" type="reset">Resetear</button>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <%- include ('./partials/footer') %>
  </body>
</html>